introSection.title: Hello And Welcome To My Website!
introSection.content: Hi there! I'm Nathan, a new alumni of the University Of British Columbia. I graduated with distinction in May 2023 with a Bachelor's of Science in Computer Science. Previously, I've worked at Letus (previously Rentmoola) for about 1.5 years as a Quality Assurance Analyst Intern. My responsibilities included performing manual testing on web applications and APIs, creating test cases, developing and maintaining automated test cases, and performing regression and smoke testing for releases.
